<P>__{(surprised)}
<D>__{i thought she built it herself.}
<C>__{rev. sullivan}
<D>__{she did. but hardly anyone does anything truly alone.}
<A>__{the reverend carries out a large cardboard postal package. landon takes it as the reverend lowers the garage door.}
<C>__{landon}
<P>__{(serious)}
<D>__{i need to do this alone.}
<A>__{reverend sullivan searches landon's face for a long moment, understanding, then turns and heads for the back door.}
